{"tid":1696283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實解決問題既方法就係解決提出問題既人外，今日見到仲有一個方法","createTime":"2019-11-06T05:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T06:00:11.000Z","uid":81236,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8c003775478cbd1db23ab654d5d0174be63f99","tid":1696283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"就係解決製造問題既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日有位香港人嘗試左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>咁做<br />\n<br />\n大家知道啦，咁樣係好暴力，會無哂民意，無左外國支持，左膠又話要割席，又話畫面唔好睇 之類<br />\n<br />\n仲會造成破窗效應<br />\n<br />\n大家都知黎黎去去都係果班人製造問題<br />\n<br />\n第日無哂問題點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解決提出問題既人，就當睇唔到問題<br />\n無哂製造問題既人，問題就唔存在了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好暴力架，唔鼓勵大家向解決製造問題既人著手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f534eab8b8471f17b1b56cebf369956eca6a5ac","tid":1696283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7978fadc5fa62516ff1ddfc469357b9ef9199f","tid":1696283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ec89f0f2191df62e6c63922c486c08c6ebf48be","tid":1696283,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}